<HEADLINE> Pilot Killed in Nevada Air Race </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	RENO, Nev. (AP) -- A plane flying in an air race crashed into a  
residential neighborhood, breaking apart and hitting cars and 
homes. The pilot was killed. 
</P>
<P>
	A young girl on the ground was treated after she was hit in the  
